name: Tiguere (Midnight)
description: If you live life by your wits and the streets are your classroom then let Tiguere be your guide. Tiguere sees opportunity where others see only failure so sharpen up your senses and go big!  Tiguere is another collectable trading card in the Los Demonios Amigos series. New cards drop every Tuesday.  Collect ‘em, trade ’em, get ‘em all! Keep an eye on Twitter for rare 1 of 1 color variants and remixes dropping randomly! Check me on IG @losdemoniosamigos and @marksarmel. Website at marksarmel.com
